alldata: sends all lists and all events and all data about them, probably little used but could be usable
changeevent: new info about an event given an id.  UPDATE events SET * WHERE user=? AND item_id=?;
newevent: new event created.  INSERT ...
finishevent: UPDATE events SET finished=True WHERE ...
unfinishevent: UPDATE events SET finished=False WHERE ...
deleteevent: removes an event entirely
eventorder: sends the order of a list of events.
newlist: INSERT ...
listorder: sends the order of the lists
changelist: to change the name of a list
deletelist: deletes a list, what do we do with events/todos? i think we should have a "trash" list for this, even if it isn't normally shown
  